     * NOTE: Construct run when owner deploy token
     * Set max total supply 80k token. Owner can't mint/generate more token more than 8k.
     * Set token name.
     * Set token symbol.
     * Set token decimals.
     * Set total supply as initial supply.
     * Set founder.
     * Add all initial token to founder.
